FBIS3-14425 "drnes059_l_94013" FBIS-NES-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 27 Mar 1994 ISRAEL IDF Officer Wounded in Terrorist Ambush TA2703052194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0505 GMT 27 Mar 94 TA2703052194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] In Gaza city yesterday, an IDF [Israel Defense Forces] officer sustained moderate to serious wounds when hit by terrorist gunfire. The terrorists fired shots from a passing car at an IDF patrol on al-Nasir street in the al-Shaykh Radwan neighborhood. The soldiers returned fire but the car managed to escape. The wounded officer was rushed by helicopter to Beersheba's Soraka Medical Center and operated upon.
